languages.text: "Хорошо. Однажды ты удивил{mf||а} меня и не сдох{mf||ла} там, а я лишился своего места. Может, и я не сдохну. Может, и ты после этого чего-то лишишься".
"Very well. Once, you surprised me. You didn't die, and I lost my status. Maybe I won't die either. Maybe you will lose something too."

languages.text: 「いいだろう。かつてお前は私を驚かせた。お前は死なず、私は地位を失った。私も死なないかも知れないし、お前も何かを失うかもしれない」
languages.original_text: "Very well. Once, you surprised me. You didn't die, and I lost my status. Maybe I won't die either. Maybe you will lose something too."

traits.locale_text: 「いいだろう。かつてお前は私を驚かせた。お前は死なず、私は地位を失った。私も死なないかも知れないし、お前も何かを失うかもしれない」
traits.speaker: Anger

languages.text: “很好。毕竟你也曾让我大吃一惊，你没死，而我却失去了我的宝座。或许下次我也不会死，或许你也会失去某些东西。”
languages.original_text: "Very well. Once, you surprised me. You didn't die, and I lost my status. Maybe I won't die either. Maybe you will lose something too."

languages.text: «Muy bien. Ya me has sorprendido antes. No moriste y yo perdí mi estatus. Tal vez yo tampoco muera y esta vez seas tú quien pierda algo».
languages.original_text: "Very well. Once, you surprised me. You didn't die, and I lost my status. Maybe I won't die either. Maybe you will lose something too."

languages.text: "Also gut. Ihr habt mich einmal überrascht. Ihr seid nicht gestorben, und ich habe meinen Status verloren. Vielleicht sterbe ich auch nicht. Vielleicht verliert auch Ihr etwas."

languages.text: « Très bien. Par le passé, vous m'avez surpris. Vous n'êtes pas {mf|mort|morte}, et moi, j'ai perdu mon statut. Peut-être que cette fois-ci, c'est moi qui ne mourrai pas et vous qui perdrez quelque chose. »

languages.text: "Öyle olsun. Daha önce beni şaşırtmıştın. Sen ölmeyince mevkimden oldum. Belki ben de ölmem. Belki sen de bir şeyler kaybedersin."

traits.locale_text: "Pekâlâ. Bir keresinde sen beni şaşırtmıştın. Sen ölmeyince mevkimden oldum. Belki ben de ölmem. Belki sen de bir şeyler kaybedersin."
